Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><strong>HTML Content Division element</strong> (<strong><code>&lt;div&gt;</code></strong>) jest&nbsp;rodzajem pojemnika na </span>treść<span class=\"seoSummary\">. Nie ma on żadnego wpływu na treść ani układ graficzny, dopóki nie zostanie ostylizowany z użyciem CSS.&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;Element&nbsp;<code>&lt;div&gt;</code>&nbsp;jako \"czysty\" pojemnik niczego nie reprezentuje. Zamiast tego, jest on używany do grupowania zawartości, dzięki czemu można go łatwo stylizować za pomocą atrybutu&nbsp;<a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes#attr-class\"><code>class</code></a> lub <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes#attr-id\"><code>id</code></a>, oznaczające część dokumentu jako napisaną w innym języku (używając&nbsp;atrybutu <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes#attr-lang\"><code>lang</code></a>), i tak dalej.</p>\n\n<table class=\"properties\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\">Kategorie zawartości</a></th>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\">Tekst lub treść osadzona</a>, namacalna zawartosć.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Dopuszczalna zawartość</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\">Tekst lub treść osadzona</a>.<br>\n    Lub (w&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/WHATWG\">WHATWG</a> HTML):&nbsp;Jeżeli rodzic jest elementem <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dl\"><code>&lt;dl&gt;</code></a>: jednego lub więcej elementów&nbsp;<a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dt\"><code>&lt;dt&gt;</code></a>, po których następuje jeden lub więcej elementów <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dd\"><code>&lt;dd&gt;</code></a>, opcjonalnie zmieszanych z elementami <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/script\"><code>&lt;script&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> i <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Pominięcie znacznika</th>\n   <td>Brak, zarówno znacznik początku, jak i końca jest obowiązkowy.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Dozwoleni rodzice&nbsp;</th>\n   <td>Każdy element akceptujący&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\">tekst lub treść osadzoną</a>.<br>\n    Lub (w&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/WHATWG\">WHATWG</a> HTML): element <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dl\"><code>&lt;dl&gt;</code></a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Wsparcie&nbsp;<a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA\">ARIA</a></th>\n   <td>Tak</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Interfejs DOM</th>\n   <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLDivElement\"><code>HTMLDivElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"atrybuty","title":"Atrybuty","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Element ten obejmuje&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes\">atrybuty globalne</a>.</p>\n\n<p>Atrybut <code>align</code> jest przestarzały; nie używaj go już dłużej. Zamiast tego należy użyć właściwości lub technik CSS takich jak <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout\">CSS Grid</a> lub&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Learn/CSS/CSS_layout/Flexbox\">CSS Flexbox</a> do wyrównania i pozycjonowania elementów <code>&lt;div&gt;</code> na stronie.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"wskazówki_dot._użytkowania","title":"Wskazówki dot. użytkowania","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Element <code>&lt;div&gt;</code> należy stosować tylko wtedy, gdy nie może go zastąpić&nbsp;żaden inny element semantyczny (np. <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article\"><code>&lt;article&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> lub&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav\"><code>&lt;nav&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>).</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przykłady","title":"Przykłady","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"prosty_przykład","title":"Prosty przykład","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Any kind of content here. Such as\n  <span class=\"token entity named-entity\" title=\"<\">&amp;lt;</span>p<span class=\"token entity named-entity\" title=\">\">&amp;gt;</span>, <span class=\"token entity named-entity\" title=\"<\">&amp;lt;</span>table<span class=\"token entity named-entity\" title=\">\">&amp;gt;</span>. You name it!<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> </code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Rezultat wygląda tak:</p>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Prosty przykład\" id=\"frame_a_simple_example\" width=\"650\" height=\"60\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/div/_sample_.a_simple_example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przykład_z_użyciem_stylów","title":"Przykład z użyciem stylów","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Ten przykład tworzy cieniowane pole, stosując styl dla&nbsp;<code>&lt;div&gt;</code> za pomocą CSS. Zwróć uwagę na użycie atrybutu <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes#attr-class\"><code>class</code></a> na elemencie <code>&lt;div&gt;</code> aby zastosować styl o nazwie <code>\"shadowbox\"</code>.</p>\n\n<h4 id=\"html\">HTML</h4>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>shadowbox<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Here's a very interesting note displayed in a\n  lovely shadowed box.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n\n<h4 id=\"css\">CSS</h4>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">.shadowbox</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 15em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1px solid #333<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">box-shadow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 8px 8px 5px #444<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 8px 12px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-image</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">linear-gradient</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>180deg<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> #fff<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> #ddd 40%<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> #ccc<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<h4 id=\"rezultat\">Rezultat</h4>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Przykład z użyciem stylów\" id=\"frame_a_styled_example\" width=\"650\" height=\"120\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/div/_sample_.a_styled_example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specyfikacje","title":"Specyfikacje","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/grouping-content.html#the-div-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"pl\">The definition of '&lt;div&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>No changes since the latest snapshot</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/grouping-content.html#the-div-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"pl\">The definition of '&lt;div&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Obsoleted <strong>align</strong></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html401/struct/global.html#h-7.5.4\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 4.01 Specification<br><small lang=\"pl\">The definition of '&lt;div&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Kompatybilność z przeglądarkami","id":"kompatybilność_z_przeglądarkami","isH3":false,"query":"html.elements.div","dataURL":"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/div/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"zobacz_także","title":"Zobacz także","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Semantic sectioning elements: <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article\"><code>&lt;article&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav\"><code>&lt;nav&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/header\"><code>&lt;header&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/footer\"><code>&lt;footer&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span\"><code>&lt;span&gt;</code></a> element for styling of phrasing content</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Atrybuty","id":"atrybuty"},{"text":"Wskazówki dot. użytkowania","id":"wskazówki_dot._użytkowania"},{"text":"Przykłady","id":"przykłady"},{"text":"Specyfikacje","id":"specyfikacje"},{"text":"Kompatybilność z przeglądarkami","id":"kompatybilność_z_przeglądarkami"},{"text":"Zobacz także","id":"zobacz_także"}],"summary":"HTML Content Division element (<div>) jest rodzajem pojemnika na . Nie ma on żadnego wpływu na treść ani układ graficzny, dopóki nie zostanie ostylizowany z użyciem CSS. ","popularity":0.0015,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<div>","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"<div>: The Content Division element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"div","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<div> : l'élément de division du contenu","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<div>: コンテンツ区分要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<div>: 콘텐츠 분할 요소","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"<div>","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"<div>: Элемент разделения контента","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"<div>：内容划分元素","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"<div>","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/web/html/element/div","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/web/html/element/div/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web","title":"Technologie Internetowe dla developerów"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"Element"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/div","title":"<div>: The Content Division element"}],"pageTitle":"<div>: The Content Division element - HTML | MDN","noIndexing":false}}